						               													<description>A fun strategic game with scary monsters from Djeco!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A challenging game where the aim is to make chains of 4 monsters in the same colour, or to surround a black monster with 3 monsters of different colour. Whenever you do one of these, you score the 4 monster cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You can play a monster next to any other monster, unless there is already a monster of the same colour on the table, in that case you have to place your monster next to the monster of the same colour (except if the monster is already surrounded by three other monsters). You must playe 1, 2, or 3 monsters each turn, and then refill you hand to 4 cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You must plan carefully, so you don't give your opponents an easy play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when the last card is played, and the player with the most scored cards wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
